{"tid":1317110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"記住：今 日 冇 人 襲 警！","createTime":"2019-07-14T17:30:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T09:19:13.000Z","uid":60231,"like":184,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"1b132d1050e344f86d83a3c5bdda62991c8053a3","tid":1317110,"uid":60231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:30:44.000Z","msg":"襲警？<br />\n邊撚度警呀？<br />\n委任證呢？！<br />\n警員編號呢？？！！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">邊撚度警呀？屌你老母！</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw, 得幾隻狗被人打實在太少太普通, 勇武加油做多Ｄ！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔駛太在意興論</span>，因為民意一早就<strong><ins>歸邊</ins></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><em>撐狗既就算開真槍都撐，唔撐既繼續撚狗</em></span><br />\n<br />\n所以TVB點煲都冇所謂, <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">文宣繼續重複返D狗既暴行就夠</span></span></strong> (E.G. 612中信立會, 旺角女途人無故被侵犯, 上水爆頭跳橋, 沙田商場出椒)<br />\n<br />\n黑狗你地大撚獲了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />開左個頭, 唔係咁易收到架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bcd84380fec39a7c54c9fed67390714278871d2","tid":1317110,"uid":60231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:32:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d8cb600e8c44464f8e2d28edd939939493daab4","tid":1317110,"uid":60231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:32:47.000Z","msg":"勇武加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2209b2d73baa00bfb13c7d07b124483e1d4063d3","tid":1317110,"uid":104621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:33:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbef105d5a587de4b1ecb1a3827988b7ea865fc0","tid":1317110,"uid":238051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:33:54.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">你扮警察\n有人冒警\n我冇嘢講\n我要搵律師</code></pre>"},{"pid":"2f04f6a1a06e623e1d772fb59b955fd1695345b4","tid":1317110,"uid":622,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:34:00.000Z","msg":"我淨係見到有熱心市民一齊制服冒警嘅可疑人物！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d4a0233f41be9ccec8ae742ac1e6642e31060b6","tid":1317110,"uid":60231,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:34:01.000Z","msg":"斷手指?? 咁咪好撚慘囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">嘻</span></span>"},{"pid":"a512f9a5a7582a74752d8b0df56ef2f81bae6678","tid":1317110,"uid":168389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:34:07.000Z","msg":"係冒警呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34cf64a68c269f1a4235f926d0d55334331a25cb","tid":1317110,"uid":60231,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2f04f6a1a06e623e1d772fb59b955fd1695345b4","tid":1317110,"uid":622,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:34:00.000Z","msg":"我淨係見到有熱心市民一齊制服冒警嘅可疑人物！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\